Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Concourse Bowling Center
Description: An affordable and safe neighbordhood bowling alley that has an arcade and bar! It is a great place to hangout with friends and family!

Name: Santa Barbara Zoo
Description: The Santa Barbara zoo is home to over 146 different species of animals! This diverse zoo is great for kids and adults who want to spend a day with the animal kingdom!

Name: Hana Kitchen
Description: This resteraunt has great options for vegans with their vegan chicken and sesame beef! It offers big healthy proportions for a good price!

Name: McConnell's Fine Ice Creams
Description: Home to some of the most distinct and fresh flavors, McConnell's is one of Santa Barbara's prized possessions! It is a must-have for hot summer days!

Name: Santa Rosa Dorm Recreational Room
Description: One of the nicest recreational rooms in UCSB! It includes a theater, pool table, air-hockey, and a ping pong table for students to relax after a stressful day!
